   =20
      Things happen
   =20
 =20

Instagram Unveils  Threads App, a Threat to Musk=E2=80=99s Twitter. (Follow=
 me on Threads!) Middle market CLOs are now private credit CLOs. Jefferies =
Sees  Turnaround in Deals After Prolonged Drought. JetBlue, Turning Focus t=
o Spirit Deal, Won=E2=80=99t Try to Save American Partnership. FTX Lawyer W=
