ortant; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #000000; border-bott=
om-style: solid; background-color: #ccc;">here is a Bloomberg News story th=
at I read this morning</a>:</p>
<blockquote>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Investigators at the Commodity Futures Trading=
 Commission have concluded that bankrupt crypto lender Celsius Network and =
its former chief executive officer broke US rules before the firm=E2=80=99s=
 implosion, according to people familiar with the matter.</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">If a majority of the CFTC=E2=80=99s commission=
ers agree with that conclusion, the agency could file a case in federal cou=
rt as soon as this month, said the people, who asked not to be identified d=
iscussing the confidential determination. Attorneys in the enforcement unit=
 determined that Celsius misled investors and should have registered with t=
he regulator, and that former CEO Alex Mashinsky also broke regulations, sa=
id one of the people. ...</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Meanwhile, the Securities and Exchange Commiss=
ion and federal prosecutors in Manhattan have also been investigating Celsi=
us, according to bankruptcy filings. Representatives for the SEC and the US=
 Attorney=E2=80=99s Office for the Southern District of New York declined t=
o comment on the status of those probes.=C2=A0</p>
</blockquote>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">How =E2=80=99bout that!</p>
